  <answer><![CDATA[<div class="c-page-content">
<p>Yes, with an average of 200 days of fresh snowfall each year between November and May, Finland has some of the best snow-sure resorts due to their location in the Arctic Circle. Inghams offer 3 great resorts for you to choose from. Skiing in Lapland is perfect for families and <a data-udi="umb://document/7b593e2c65884305ba057ea8fb4ca82a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7b593e2c65884305ba057ea8fb4ca82a}" title="Skiing in Lapland for beginners">beginners</a> looking for gentle slopes, and for those looking to try something a little different, cross country skiing is available in all three resorts - <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Ylläs</a> &amp; <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselkä</a>.</p>
</div>]]></answer>
